{"type": "article", "id": 13764, "title": "Christian Louboutin 口红", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-20T07:45:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000302LFJcI1T27kCKlaiX.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日，红鞋底 Christian Louboutin 进军美妆界推出的口红终于来了，和他们之前推出的指甲油包装一样，经典的 “Louboutin 红色”采用子弹头黑色包装，而其他颜色使用金色包装，目前一共有 38 种颜色，一共有三种质地，分别是光泽缎面，丝绒哑光和薄纱哑光。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141441s2HMloqQ6SunLvtd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2002924\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141442rzXwaLjR9cOBWhos.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141442PouOsThWp1L0r3nM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66129032\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}